name: Cool
description:
The first collector of this NFT will receive this original painting. 1st collector, please DM me via Twitter @Maks_Denysenko & I'll send you the painting!

Cool
At one time, I ordered 10 boxes of mtn water based spraypaint from Germany.
The paint is non-toxic, so it is best suited for art therapy sessions with children. After working with the children, I couldn't stand it and took the paint, came to the center, bought canvas and boards, stretched the canvas right on the street and wrote this wonderful work.

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2020, 200x80 cm spray paint on canvas, 2061x4601
